    {%- comment -%}
      LCP: preload first slideshow hero image.
      Desktop: Prestige requests _{width}x where width ≈ viewport. 1200x covers most desktop breakpoints.
      Mobile:  mob02_x800.jpg is the mobile first-slide image.
      Update URLs if slideshow images change (section 1576022810447).
